          "name": "Borewyrm Infestation",
          "description": "Twice per battle, at the end of your opponent’s turn, if this model is not within Engagement Range of one or more enemy units, you can remove this model from the battlefield. In the Reinforcements step of your next Movement phase, set it up anywhere on the battlefield that\nis more than 9\" horizontally away from all enemy models. If the battle ends and this unit is not on the battlefield, it is destroyed. \n\nDesigner’s Note: Place two Borewyrm Infestation tokens next to this model, removing one each time this ability has been used."
        }
